Text.val: Bijhouden van sessies en ophalen proces instellingen

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from product_fee_lines l inner join product_fee_settings s on s.id = l.pfs_id inner join producten_per_relatie p on p.ppr_id = s.ppr_id inner join clienten c on c.cl_nummer = p.ppr_relatienummer inner join doorbelberekend_vw d on d.db_clientnummer = p.ppr_relatienummer and d.db_productnummer = p.ppr_productnummer and d.db_volgnr_per_product = p.ppr_volgnr_per_product where p.ppr_relatienummer between ~1 and ~2 and p.ppr_productnummer between ~3 and ~4 and ((~5=1 and p.ppr_volgnr_per_product between ~6 and ~7) or ~5=0) and c.cl_clientgroep between ~8 and ~9 and d.db_datum_zoeken = ~10 and d.db_soort_berekening = ~11 and d.db_maand_jaar_tabel = ~12 and d.db_proforma = ~13 and d.db_doorbel_status >= 1 and d.db_status_record <> 3

select count(distinct p.ppr_id) "NMBR_OF_EXTERNAL_RECORDS" from product_fee_lines l inner join product_fee_settings s on s.id = l.pfs_id inner join producten_per_relatie p on p.ppr_id = s.ppr_id inner join clienten c on c.cl_nummer = p.ppr_relatienummer inner join doorbelberekend_vw d on d.db_clientnummer = p.ppr_relatienummer and d.db_productnummer = p.ppr_productnummer and d.db_volgnr_per_product = p.ppr_volgnr_per_product where p.ppr_relatienummer between ~1 and ~2 and p.ppr_productnummer between ~3 and ~4 and ((~5=1 and p.ppr_volgnr_per_product between ~6 and ~7) or ~5=0) and c.cl_clientgroep between ~8 and ~9 and d.db_datum_zoeken = ~10 and d.db_soort_berekening = ~11 and d.db_maand_jaar_tabel = ~12 and d.db_proforma = ~13 and d.db_doorbel_status >= 1 and d.db_status_record <> 3 and d.db_status_record <> 5 and d.db_status_record <> 9 and l.incasso_method=8 and d.CALCULATION_VARIANT=1

select B.RELNR from ( select rownum my_row, A.RELNR from ( select p.ppr_relatienummer relnr from product_fee_lines l inner join product_fee_settings s on s.id = l.pfs_id inner join producten_per_relatie p on p.ppr_id = s.ppr_id inner join clienten c on c.cl_nummer = p.ppr_relatienummer inner join doorbelberekend_vw d on d.db_clientnummer = p.ppr_relatienummer and d.db_productnummer = p.ppr_productnummer and d.db_volgnr_per_product = p.ppr_volgnr_per_product where p.ppr_relatienummer between ~1 and ~2 and p.ppr_productnummer between ~3 and ~4 and ((~5=1 and p.ppr_volgnr_per_product between ~6 and ~7) or ~5=0) and c.cl_clientgroep between ~8 and ~9 and d.db_datum_zoeken = ~10 and d.db_soort_berekening = ~11 and d.db_maand_jaar_tabel = ~12 and d.db_proforma = ~13 and d.db_doorbel_status >= 1 and d.db_status_record <> 3 order by p.ppr_relatienummer asc)A ) B where MOD(B.my_row,~14)=0
